 'unitsize is 20 for pixels, 1 for tiles
 
 aheadxy x, y, direction, distance
 
 IF gmap(5) = 1 THEN
  wrapxy x, y, mapsizetiles.x * unitsize, mapsizetiles.y * unitsize
